INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 1.0.1 (2022-04-05)
E: Ensure compatibility with Ansible 2.14.0 and Jinja2 >= 3.0.0

* Version 1.0.0 (2021-12-18)
C: Add support for Debian 11 (Bullseye)
C: Drop support for Debian 10 (Buster)

* Version 0.9.0 (2021-12-05)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.3.1

* Version 0.8.0 (2021-11-18)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.3.0

* Version 0.7.0 (2021-08-07)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.2.2

* Version 0.6.0 (2021-08-05)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.2.1

* Version 0.5.0 (2021-07-17)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.2.0

* Version 0.4.0 (2021-03-06)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.1.2

* Version 0.3.0 (2021-02-13)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.1.1

* Version 0.2.0 (2021-02-08)
F: Update node_exporter to version 1.1.0

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-12-20)
